27:53.205 --> 27:54.907
- Uh-uh.
- Yeah.

27:54.907 --> 27:56.242
- No.
- Yes.

27:56.242 --> 27:58.444
Walk away, girl.

28:22.401 --> 28:24.871
Hello.

28:26.572 --> 28:28.574
