28:32.244 --> 28:34.847
- What's your name?
- Emma Jean.

28:34.847 --> 28:37.116
Well, hi, Emma Jean.

28:37.116 --> 28:39.585
Where'd you come from?

28:39.585 --> 28:42.254
Oh, I came from California.

28:42.254 --> 28:44.957
You know where that is?

28:44.957 --> 28:47.259
No.

28:47.259 --> 28:50.262
Hollywood. Disneyland.

28:50.262 --> 28:52.398
No.

28:52.398 --> 28:54.566
Maybe you could
go there some day.

28:57.970 --> 29:00.139
Why not?

29:12.151 --> 29:14.353
Isn't that the reverend
tow truck guy?

29:18.324 --> 29:20.492
You guys met Terry, huh?

29:20.492 --> 29:23.896
He seems like a popular guy.

29:23.896 --> 29:26.465
Yeah, well, that's my
big brother for ya.

29:26.465 --> 29:29.168
Seriously?

29:29.168 --> 29:32.004
One and only.

29:32.004 --> 29:33.572
Hell of a guy.

29:40.012 --> 29:43.415
Hey, I'm tired. Ready to go?

29:43.415 --> 29:44.616
I guess so.

29:46.585 --> 29:50.456
Mack, it has been a pleasure.

29:50.456 --> 29:52.358
Till we meet again.

29:52.358 --> 29:53.692
I look forward to it.

29:53.692 --> 29:55.094
Thanks.

30:01.968 --> 30:04.003
Grill still open?

30:14.146 --> 30:16.082
Not these two.

30:16.082 --> 30:17.602
I don't know
what you're talking about.

30:20.386 --> 30:23.222
Just leave them alone.

30:23.222 --> 30:24.690
You think I have designs
on every traveler

30:24.690 --> 30:26.225
who comes through this town?

30:26.225 --> 30:29.395
I can tell when you see
an opportunity.

30:29.395 --> 30:31.097
You can tell that just
by looking at me?

30:31.097 --> 30:32.364
Huh.

30:34.066 --> 30:36.402
I guess that's what happens
when two people

30:36.402 --> 30:39.038
spend so much time together.

30:41.407 --> 30:44.410
You remember why we're here
in the first place?

30:44.410 --> 30:47.146
Or did that detail
slip your mind?

30:52.018 --> 30:54.386
So, what did you tell them?

30:57.156 --> 30:58.524
Nothing.

30:59.725 --> 31:01.627
That was very kind of you.

31:06.398 --> 31:09.335
