31:09.335 --> 31:12.138
In spite of the fact that I saw
you talking to those girls?

31:13.739 --> 31:15.107
Look, I swear, I...

31:15.107 --> 31:17.776
Do you understand
that it hurts me

31:17.776 --> 31:20.312
when you won't simply
tell me what it is

31:20.312 --> 31:22.448
you spoke to those girls about?

31:27.619 --> 31:30.622
Well, that wasn't so bad.

31:30.622 --> 31:32.991
Yeah.

31:34.460 --> 31:37.329
Hey, you remember
the emergency reserve?

31:37.329 --> 31:38.664
Yes.

31:38.664 --> 31:41.533
I believe this qualifies
as an emergency.

31:42.634 --> 31:44.036
I thought you'd never ask.

31:52.144 --> 31:54.446
* bring a book
a page is nameless *

