01:14:02.105 --> 01:14:03.873
Don't lie to me. Just tell me.

01:14:07.176 --> 01:14:09.879
That...

01:14:09.879 --> 01:14:12.882
Last year at my birthday

01:14:12.882 --> 01:14:15.251
when you guys
got in that huge fight...

01:14:17.687 --> 01:14:19.022
