01:15:15.745 --> 01:15:17.146
Shannon, please stay.

01:15:18.848 --> 01:15:20.183
Where're you going?

01:15:22.418 --> 01:15:23.887
Fuck.

01:16:01.290 --> 01:16:03.159
Hey.

01:16:03.159 --> 01:16:04.728
Something wrong?

01:16:06.963 --> 01:16:09.866
